\c 3
\s Iminikelo yokuthula
\p
\v 1 Uba-ke umnikelo wakhe ungumhlatshelo weminikelo yokuthula\x + 7.11,29. 17.5. 22.21.\x*, nxa enikela okwenkomo, ingabe iduna kumbe insikazi, uzawunikela ungelasici phambi kweN\nd kosi\x + 1.3.\x*\nd*.
\v 2 Uzabeka isandla sakhe enhlokweni yomnikelo wakhe\x + 1.4.\x*, awuhlabe emnyango wethente lenhlangano; amadodana kaAroni angabapristi azafafaza-ke igazi phezu kwelathi inhlangothi zonke.
\v 3 Uzanikela okuvela kuwo umhlatshelo weminikelo yokuthula umnikelo owenzelwe iN\nd kosi\nd* ngomlilo, idanga\x + 4.8,9.\x*, lamahwahwa wonke asemibilini,
\v 4 lezinso zombili lamahwahwa akuzo asezinkalweni, lamahwahwa angaphezu kwesibindi uzawasusa lezinso.
\v 5 Njalo amadodana kaAroni azawatshisa elathini phezu komnikelo wokutshiswa ophezu kwenkuni eziphezu komlilo\x + 6.12.\x*; kungumnikelo owenziwe ngomlilo oloqhatshi olumnandi eN\nd kosi\nd*ni.
\p
\v 6 Uba-ke umnikelo wakhe ongumhlatshelo weminikelo yokuthula eN\nd kosi\nd*ni ungowomhlambi, iduna kumbe insikazi, uzawunikela ungelasici\x + 3.1,\x*.
\v 7 Uba enikela iwundlu, libe ngumnikelo wakhe, uzalinikela phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*,
\v 8 abeke isandla sakhe enhlokweni yomnikelo wakhe, awuhlabe phambi kwethente lenhlangano; amadodana kaAroni azafafaza-ke igazi lawo phezu kwelathi inhlangothi zonke.
\v 9 Uzanikela okuvela kuwo umhlatshelo weminikelo yokuthula, umnikelo owenzelwe iN\nd kosi\nd* ngomlilo, amahwahwa awo, umsila wonke ononileyo ewuquma eduze lomgogodla\x + Eks. 29.22; 9.19.\x*, ledanga, lamahwahwa wonke asemibilini,
\v 10 lezinso zombili lamahwahwa akuzo asezinkalweni, lamahwahwa angaphezu kwesibindi uzawasusa lezinso.
\v 11 Umpristi uzakutshisa-ke elathini, kuyikudla komnikelo owenzelwe iN\nd kosi\nd* ngomlilo\x + 3.16; 21.6,8,17,21,22; 22.7,11,13,25. Hez. 44.7. Mal. 1.7.\x*.
\p
\v 12 Uba-ke umnikelo wakhe uyimbuzi, uzawunikela phambi kweN\nd kosi\x + 3.1,7.\x*\nd*,
\v 13 abeke isandla sakhe enhlokweni yayo, ayihlabe phambi kwethente lenhlangano; amadodana kaAroni azafafaza-ke igazi layo phezu kwelathi inhlangothi zonke.
\v 14 Uzanikela okuvela kiyo umnikelo wakhe, umnikelo owenzelwe iN\nd kosi\nd* ngomlilo, idanga, lamahwahwa wonke asemibilini,
\v 15 lezinso zombili lamahwahwa akuzo asezinkalweni, lamahwahwa angaphezu kwesibindi uzawasusa lezinso.
\v 16 Njalo umpristi uzakutshisa elathini, kuyikudla komnikelo owenziwe ngomlilo, kube luqhatshi olumnandi. Wonke amahwahwa ngaweN\nd kosi\x + 7.23,25. 1 Sam. 2.15.\x*\nd*.
\v 17 Yisimiso saphakade ezizukulwaneni zenu\x + 6.18,22. 7.34,36. 10.9,15. 16.29,31,34. 17.7. 23.14,21,31,41. 24.3,9.\x*, emizini yenu yonke, \add sokuthi\add* lingadli ngitsho amahwahwa lagazi\x + Gen. 9.4. Levi 7.26; 17.10-14; 19.26. Dute. 12.16,23; 15.23. 1 Sam. 14.33. Hez. 44.7,15. Seb. 15.20,29.\x*.
